HTML::Hyphenate version 0.100
=============================

This module can be used to insert soft hyphens into HTML.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Build.PL
   ./Build
   ./Build test
   ./Build install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Moose
  Encode
  HTML::Entities
  HTML::TreeBuilder    anything but 4.0
  Log::Log4perl
  Readonly 	       1.03
  Set::Scalar
  TeX::Hyphen
  TeX::Hyphen::Pattern
  Test::More	       0.86
  Test::NoWarnings
  version

